  "prompt": "Can I use a Samsung Galaxy On5 with the Gear VR?",
  "response": "The Samsung Galaxy On5 is not compatible with the Gear VR. The Gear VR is designed to work with specific Samsung Galaxy models, mainly the flagship series such as the Galaxy S6, S7, S8, S9, S10, Note 5, Note 8, and Note 9, as well as some other high-end models. The Galaxy On5, being a budget-friendly device, does not meet the hardware requirements for the Gear VR. If you're interested in using a virtual reality headset, you might want to consider other options like Google Cardboard, which is compatible with a wider range of smartphones.",
